text: Bodenheim is a state-recognized tourism municipality (Fremdenverkehrsgemeinde) in the Mainz-Bingen district of Rhineland-Palatinate, Germany. Bodenheim may also refer to: *Bodenheim (Verbandsgemeinde), a collective municipality in the German district of Mainz-Bingen, encompassing the tourism municipality People: *Maxwell Bodenheim (1892–1954), American poet and novelist. *Nelly Bodenheim (1874–1951), Dutch illustrator ==See also== *Bodenheimer, a surname
